						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up in front of the Sōmaliṅgēśvara temple in the village.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1209, Vyaya, Chaitra śu. 1, Thursday.</p>						

						<p>Highly damaged. Seems to records the gift of tolls for burning a perpetual lamp.</p>						

